{"tid":50231,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"仆街頭先落過雲雨叫左炒蛋","createTime":"2016-12-22T09:14:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T02:47:37.000Z","uid":65354,"like":3,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f5dc6a5b44007dc96ca2e18a2fb145fee3b8851","tid":50231,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:14:25.000Z","msg":"屌 頭先食tea果陣叫左個常餐跟炒蛋，冇留意原來出面無啦啦落緊雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n想截番張單已經見到個哥仔陰陰嘴笑拎左碟蛋出黎俾我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食完冇乜野 可能係只係過雲雨,個師傅放我一馬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n又或者係因為太旺市 如果唔係真係冇命開po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90a122bbb8bdea4ba7b2aa3b38e7b93d3e4a3f6e","tid":50231,"uid":42425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:14:59.000Z","msg":"哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b36c19a46e25bd41b84b238a25c8424114c9025d","tid":50231,"uid":11977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:15:33.000Z","msg":"好撚好笑 屌你老母"},{"pid":"48836ba47191b60e3158453f46877b6a5a2d9277","tid":50231,"uid":1977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:15:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n哈哈哈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"620bc737d4023f1f566f749d18cb068acb4dd0ed","tid":50231,"uid":60020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:15:58.000Z","msg":"寫定遺書"},{"pid":"82b7f9123a3faa253b7a504ad72ab0730b127844","tid":50231,"uid":65354,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T09:16:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>寫定遺書</blockquote><br />\n真心驚撚到 一邊食一邊手震<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"717451b57b3a2a32813a946428a1cfc285